<div class="h-full flex">
  <div class="flex flex-col min-w-0 flex-1 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex-1 relative z-0 flex overflow-hidden">
      <main class="flex-1 relative z-0 overflow-y-auto focus:outline-none xl:order-last">
        <article>
          <div>
            <div>
              <img class="h-32 w-full object-cover lg:h-48" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/drg9hguhu/image/upload/w_1000,ar_16:9,c_fill,g_auto,e_sharpen/v1659354131/comix/erik-mclean-tNO5weLNt-E-unsplash.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
              <div class="-mt-12 sm:-mt-16 sm:flex sm:items-end sm:space-x-5">
                <div class="avatar flex">
                  <div class="w-36 rounded-full">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1463453091185-61582044d556?ixlib=rb-=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=8&w=1024&h=1024&q=80" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 sm:flex-1 sm:min-w-0 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-end sm:space-x-6 sm:pb-1">
                  <div class="sm:hidden 2xl:block mt-6 min-w-0 flex-1">
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 truncate">
                        <%= @creator_profile.name %>
                    </h1>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden sm:block 2xl:hidden mt-6 min-w-0 flex-1">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 truncate">
                    <%= @creator_profile.name %>
                </h1>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tabs -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-2 2xl:mt-5">
            <div class="border-b border-gray-200">
              <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <nav class="-mb-px flex space-x-8" aria-label="Tabs">
                  <a href="#" class="border-cx-purple text-gray-900 whitespace-nowrap py-4 px-1 border-b-2 font-bold text-lg" aria-current="page"> Profile </a>
                </nav>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-4 gap-y-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="sm:col-span-1">
                <dt class="text-xl font-bold ">Email</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                    <%= mail_to @creator_profile.user.email %>
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="sm:col-span-1">
                <dt class="text-xl font-bold ">Skill</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-md text-gray-900"><%= @creator_profile.skills %></dd>
              </div>

              <div class="sm:col-span-1">
                <dt class="text-xl font-bold ">Website</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                  <%= link_to @creator_profile.website, @creator_profile.website %>
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="sm:col-span-1">
                <dt class="text-xl font-bold">Social</dt>
                <div class="flex flex-row">
                  <dd class="mt-1 mx-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                    <% if @creator_profile.twitter %>
                      <%= link_to  "https://twitter.com" do %>
                        <ion-icon name="logo-twitter"></ion-icon>
                      <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                  </dd>
                  <dd class="mt-1 mx-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                    <% if @creator_profile.facebook %>
                      <%= link_to  "https://facebook.com" do %>
                        <ion-icon name="logo-facebook"></ion-icon>
                      <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                  </dd>
                  <dd class="mt-1 mx-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                    <% if @creator_profile.instagram %>
                      <%= link_to  "https://instagram.com" do %>
                        <ion-icon name="logo-instagram"></ion-icon>
                      <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                  </dd>
                  <dd class="mt-1 mx-1 text-md text-gray-900">
                    <% if @creator_profile.instagram %>
                      <%= link_to  "https://tiktok.com" do %>
                        <ion-icon name="logo-tiktok"></ion-icon>
                      <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                  </dd>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <dt class="text-lg font-bold ">About</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 max-w-prose text-md text-gray-900 space-y-5">
                  <p>Tincidunt quam neque in cursus viverra orci, dapibus nec tristique. Nullam ut sit dolor consectetur urna, dui cras nec sed. Cursus risus congue arcu aenean posuere aliquam.</p>
                  <p>Et vivamus lorem pulvinar nascetur non. Pulvinar a sed platea rhoncus ac mauris amet. Urna, sem pretium sit pretium urna, senectus vitae. Scelerisque fermentum, cursus felis dui suspendisse velit pharetra. Augue et duis cursus maecenas eget quam lectus. Accumsan vitae nascetur pharetra rhoncus praesent dictum risus suspendisse.</p>
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="sm:col-span-2">
                <dt class="text-lg font-bold ">Products</dt>
                <dd class="flex flex-row">
                  <%= render "projects/product_card" %>
                  <%= render "projects/product_card" %>
                </dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
